<section id="section2">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
            <h2 class="colour2">What can TYK offer your family?</h2>
            <span class="bg-colour1"></span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="wrapper bg-colour2">
        <div class="container">
            <ul>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/4a72da19d8ef84023d10ae8a6fa38828.png" alt="SIS offers icon-6" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">ESF Network</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>As part of the English Schools Foundation(ESF), our students are supported by the largest English-medium international school organisation in Hong Kong, providing them the resources and opportunities not found outside of ESF Schools.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://tyk.esf.edu.hk/en/about_us/ESF_family/">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/e21093779c5be02070342f26bb967f35.png" alt="Real-world Experience" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">Holistic Learning Approach</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>Our dedicated, experienced educators provide personalised learning in a supportive and nurturing environment.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://tyk.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/our_approach/">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/64f2668cf25dbfb73d755c7af63aecf5.png" alt="Comprehensive Student Support" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">Experienced and Caring Educators</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>Our dedicated teachers provide personalised attention, fostering a supportive and nurturing environment.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://tyk.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_people/our_team/">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/4fc1f6e2a57a30cc64430db653072412.png" alt="Multicultural Environment" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">Welcoming Community</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>Your child will thrive in a diverse and inclusive community, learning with a global perspective.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://tyk.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/student_support_Wellbeing/">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/5f2f57088a1ba8b7cddadfb361215028.png" alt="Well-rounded Education" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">Enriching Learning Environment</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>Open-plan areas foster community, connection, and exploration in stimulating indoor and outdoor learning spaces.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://tyk.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_experiences/learning_environment/">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/d6e756e66ebaacccd32daa5690d32498.png" alt="Strong School-Family Connection" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">Strong Parent Partnership</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>We actively involve parents in their child's learning journey, ensuring they feel part of our collaborative early learning community.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://tyk.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_people/parent_partnerships/">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script type="text/javascript">
        $(window).load(function() {
            $('h3', '#section2').each(function() {
                let img = $(this).parent().children('img');
                if(img.length) {
                    $(this).css('top', img.offset().top + img.height() + 25 - $(this).parent().offset().top);
                }
            });
        });
    </script>
</section>
<section id="section3">
    <img src="/cache/img/9cee734dc3a19fcf9e464f1ea9d4896c.jpg" alt="tsingyi_esf_1597" loading="lazy" width="1722" height="1294" />    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="section-title-container">
            <div class="section-title">
                <h2 class="colour2">Academics</h2>
                <span class="bg-colour1"></span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="tabs">
                            <button class="tab current" data-id="1">Teaching and Learning</button>
                            <button class="tab" data-id="2">Support for Learning Diversity</button>
                    </div>
        <select class="tab-select" name="tab"><option value="1">Teaching and Learning</option><option value="2">Support for Learning Diversity</option></select>                    <div class="tab-content current" data-id="1">
                                <article class="editor"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We provide a caring, supportive, and enriching environment for your child to nurture their abilities and talents. Our play-based approach to inquiry encourages curiosity, creativity, and the development of communication and social skills. Focusing on fun and relevant experiences, we aim to instil a lifelong love of learning. Children can be independent and inquisitive in their learning.</span></p></article>
                                    <a href="https://tyk.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/our_approach/">
                        <span>Find out more</span>
                    </a>
                            </div>
                    <div class="tab-content" data-id="2">
                                <article class="editor"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We prioritise skill development for all students. We offer personalised learning opportunities to accommodate each child on their learning journey. Our experienced teachers are supported by our Student Support Coordinator and ESF Student Support Services Team.</span></p></article>
                                    <a href="https://tyk.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/student_support_Wellbeing/">
                        <span>Find out more</span>
                    </a>
                            </div>
                <script type="text/javascript">
            $(document).ready(function() {
                $('.select .select-container div:nth-child(' + ($('.tab.current', '#section3').index() + 1) + ')', '#section3').hide();

                $('.tab', '#section3').click(function() {
                    $('.tab, .tab-content', '#section3').removeClass('current');
                    $(this).addClass('current');
                    $('.tab-content[data-id=' + $(this).data('id') + ']', '#section3').addClass('current');
                    $('select', '#section3').val($(this).data('id')).selectbox('refresh');
                    $('.select .select-container div', '#section3').show();
                    $('.select .select-container div:nth-child(' + ($('.tab.current', '#section3').index() + 1) + ')', '#section3').hide();
                });

                $('.tab-select', '#section3').change(function() {
                    $('.tab, .tab-content', '#section3').removeClass('current');
                    $('.tab[data-id=' + $(this).val() + ']').addClass('current');
                    $('.tab-content[data-id=' + $(this).val() + ']', '#section3').addClass('current');
                    $('.select .select-container div', '#section3').show();
                    $('.select .select-container div:nth-child(' + ($('.tab.current', '#section3').index() + 1) + ')', '#section3').hide();
                });
            });
        </script>
    </div>
</section>
